<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-93-0718 </DOCNO><TEXT>Designed for both new and seasoned authors, this paper covers not onlythe basics of writing a paper but also how to submit a paper for publicationand what to expect during the publication process. The course is dividedinto four sections: (1) writing a paper in radiology; (2) selecting appropriateindex terms or key words; (3) manuscript submission, the peer reviewprocess, and manuscript revision; and (4) the publication process.</TEXT></DOC>